OL,3,CFamily left with #200,000 bill due to
OL,4,C'broken' young-onset dementia care
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FBut Erin says despite assurances from
OL,8,FBetsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,9,FBoard that he would likely receive
OL,10,Ffinancial support due to the
OL,11,Fcomplexity of his condition, no such
OL,12,Fhelp came.
OL,14,FAfter receiving a diagnosis of FTD in
OL,15,F2021, Tony needed full-time care and
OL,16,Fthe only local options for him was in
OL,17,Fan independent living facility on
OL,18,FAnglesey - this came at a cost of
OL,19,F#12,000 a month for the first year.
