OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FThese fees increased to #24,000 a
OL,8,Fmonth in the second year as his
OL,9,Fcondition deteriorated.
OL,11,F"I think altogether it cost Dad around
OL,12,F#250,000," Erin told S4C's flagship
OL,13,Fcurrent affairs programme, Y Byd ar
OL,14,FBedwar.
OL,16,F"We sold his home to cover the costs,
OL,17,Fbut in the end we ran out of money."
