OL,4,C'broken' young-onset dementia care
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FAccording to Erin, Tony continued to
OL,8,Freceive care despite her warnings to
OL,9,Fthe authorities that his money was
OL,10,Frunning out. This has resulted in care
OL,11,Fcosts of #200,000 that are outstanding.
OL,13,F"The financial impact has been huge on
OL,14,Fdad and I," explained Erin, who is
OL,15,Ftaking anti-anxiety medication to cope
OL,16,Fwith the stress and who says that the
OL,17,Fsituation could have been avoided
OL,18,Fentirely.
