OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FLast year, Erin discovered that an
OL,8,Fapplication for financial support for
OL,9,FTony, called 'Continuing Healthcare
OL,10,FFunding' (CHC) was never completed by
OL,11,FBetsi Cadwaladr University Health
OL,12,FBoard.
OL,14,FShe also says that Anglesey County
OL,15,FCouncil had not verified how long Tony
OL,16,Fcould pay for his care. Erin strongly
OL,17,Fbelieves that both of these steps
OL,18,Fcould have prevented her from being in
OL,19,Fthe position she now finds herself in.
