OL,7,F"I depended on the professionals. I
OL,8,Ftrusted them," she said. "But in the
OL,9,Fend, they let us down."
OL,11,F'A postcode lottery in care'
OL,13,FDr Catrin Hedd Jones, a dementia
OL,14,Fspecialist who advises the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment, says Erin's experience is
OL,16,Fnot unusual.
