OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"We hear far too often about families
OL,8,Fgoing through these terrible
OL,9,Fexperiences - people living with
OL,10,Fdementia who aren't getting the care
OL,11,Fthey need and are having to pay huge
OL,12,Fsums for it," she said.
OL,14,F"There are fantastic, innovative
OL,15,Fservices in some areas, but many
OL,16,Ffamilies can't access them purely
OL,17,Fbecause of where they live. It's what
OL,18,FI'd call 'a postcode lottery,' and
OL,19,Fthat's unacceptable."
