OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FIt is estimated that around 3,700 in
OL,8,FWales are currently living with young-
OL,9,Fonset dementia, which is when symptoms
OL,10,Fbegin before 65 years old.
OL,12,FWhile Cardiff and the Vale University
OL,13,FHealth Board run a specialist "Cariad
OL,14,FUnit" for younger people with
OL,15,Fdementia, it remains the only such
OL,16,Ffacility in Wales. There is no
OL,17,Fequivalent provision in north Wales.
OL,26,@uD@_OUvD@EO]
