OL,7,FFollowing an official complaint by
OL,8,FErin, Betsi Cadwaladr University
OL,9,FHealth Board apologised for not
OL,10,Ffollowing procedures around Continuing
OL,11,FHealthcare Care (CHC) assessments,
OL,12,Fthat could have enabled her father to
OL,13,Fbe assessed for financial support.
