OL,7,FIn a statement to Y Byd ar Bedwar, the
OL,8,FHealth Board's Executive Director of
OL,9,FAllied Health Professionals and Health
OL,10,FScience, Teresa Owen said: "We
OL,11,Funderstand and sympathise with family
OL,12,Fmembers trying to negotiate Continuing
OL,13,FHealthcare Care (CHC) assessments for
OL,14,Floved ones.
