OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,F"In this case, we would like to
OL,8,Fapologise again for the failings found
OL,9,Fin the confidential report. While I'm
OL,10,Fpleased the report highlighted the
OL,11,Fappropriate care Mr Thomas received,
OL,12,Fwe didn't give Miss Thomas the
OL,13,Finformation and guidance she was
OL,14,Fentitled to around CHC.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
