OL,7,FIn a statement, the council said the
OL,8,Fsituation was "complex," and that it
OL,9,Fcontinues to liaise with the family,
OL,10,Fbut that it would not be appropriate
OL,11,Fto comment further while legal
OL,12,Fprocesses are ongoing.
OL,14,FTony now lives in a care home near
OL,15,FCaernarfon, this time funded by the
OL,16,FHealth Board and Local Authority. Erin
OL,17,Fis now working with a solicitor to see
OL,18,Fwhether the Health board and local
OL,19,Fcouncil can reimburse some of her
OL,20,Ffather's care costs to help clear some
OL,21,Fof the debt.
